    <main>
        <section id="about" class="container section-padding">
            <h3>About Me</h3>
            <p>Highly analytical and detail-oriented Information Technology professional (BSIT, Cum Laude) with cumulative experience spanning Service Desk Operations and Network Operations Center (NOC) environments. Proven track record in real-time system monitoring (Grafana), technical troubleshooting, and incident lifecycle management using ITIL v4 frameworks and Jira ticketing systems.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="experience" class="container section-padding bg-light">
            <h3>Professional Experience</h3>
            <div class="job">
                <h4>Service Desk / NOC Engineer</h4>
                <p class="company">NCS PH (Formerly Yondu Inc.) | Feb 2025 – Present</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Monitor enterprise-level network infrastructure and critical system alerts using NMS tools like Grafana to ensure 24/7/365 operational uptime.</li>
                    <li>Manage technical incidents and service requests using Jira Service Desk, adhering to SLA guidelines.</li>
                    <li>Perform Tier-1 technical troubleshooting for network connectivity and system bottlenecks.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="job">
                <h4>Process Executive</h4>
                <p class="company">Infosys BPM | Mar 2024 – Jan 2025</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Delivered cross-platform technical assistance to global users, resolving system access errors.</li>
                    <li>Logged and tracked high-priority escalations via enterprise ticketing software.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="projects" class="container section-padding">
            <h3>Featured Projects</h3>
            <div class="project-grid">
                <div class="project-card">
                    <h4>Python Network Uptime Monitor</h4>
                    <p>A lightweight Python script utilizing ping libraries to monitor remote server availability and log latency metrics locally, demonstrating automated infrastructure monitoring.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card">
                    <h4>Sagada Hike Itinerary Tracker</h4>
                    <p>An interactive, responsive HTML/CSS/JS web application designed to track camping gear, budget, and a three-day itinerary for a Mt. Kupapey hiking expedition.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card">
                    <h4>Motorcycle Maintenance Log</h4>
                    <p>A basic C# and SQL backend application built to track motorcycle service packages, oil changes, and custom hardware modifications.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

